## File Placement Guidelines

| Type | Location | Example |
|------|----------|---------|
| Feature DTOs | `features/<feature>/data/models/` | `user_dto.dart` |
| Feature Enums | `features/<feature>/data/models/` | `user_enums.dart` |
| Feature Repos | `features/<feature>/data/` | `auth_repository.dart` |
| Domain Models | `features/<feature>/domain/models/` | `user.dart` |
| Use Cases | `features/<feature>/domain/use_cases/` | `login_user_use_case.dart` |
| Providers | `features/<feature>/presentation/providers/` | `auth_provider.dart` |
| Screens | `features/<feature>/presentation/screens/` | `login_screen.dart` |
| Feature Widgets | `features/<feature>/presentation/widgets/` | `login_form.dart` |
| Shared Widgets | `core/widgets/` | `refreshable_content.dart` |
| API Services | `core/api/services/` | `auth_service.dart` |
| Global Providers | `core/providers/` | `locale_provider.dart` |

