## Core Directory Details

### `core/api/`
- `services/` - Chopper service definitions (`.dart` + `.chopper.dart`)
- `models/` - Shared API DTOs and enums
- `models/enum/` - Shared enums (`application_enums.dart`, `boolean_flag.dart`)
- `interceptors/` - HTTP interceptors (`auth_interceptor.dart`, `header_interceptor.dart`)
- `converters/` - Response converters (`built_value_converter.dart`)
- `serializers/` - Custom plugins (`int_to_bool_plugin.dart`, `string_to_number_plugin.dart`)
- `errors/` - API error handling (`api_errors.dart`)
- `serializers.dart` - Built Value serializers config
- `api_client.dart` - Chopper client setup

### `core/domain/`
- `result.dart` - Result<T> pattern for error handling
- `paginated_list.dart` - Reusable pagination model

### `core/presentation/providers/`
- `base_notifier.dart` - Base for non-paginated features
- `base_state.dart` - Reusable state for non-paginated
- `paginated_notifier.dart` - Base for paginated features
- `paginated_state.dart` - Reusable state for paginated

### `core/providers/`
- `api_config_provider.dart` - API configuration + `sharedPreferencesProvider`
- `locale_provider.dart` - Locale management with persistence
- `fcm_provider.dart` - Firebase Cloud Messaging

### `core/storage/`
- `credentials_storage.dart` - Secure credentials storage

### `core/widgets/`
- `refreshable_content.dart` - Pull-to-refresh wrapper
- `paginated_list_view.dart` - Infinite scroll list
- `error_state_widget.dart` - Error display
- `loading_state_widget.dart` - Loading indicator
- `card_container.dart` - Styled card wrapper
- `dashboard_card.dart` - Dashboard card component
- `icon_container.dart` - Icon with background
- `input_field.dart` - Styled text field
- `primary_button.dart` - Primary button
- `status_badge.dart` - Status indicator
- `stat_item.dart` - Statistics display
- `language_toggle.dart` - AR/EN switcher

