## Routing (GoRouter)

Routes defined in `lib/main.dart`:

```dart
final routerProvider = Provider<GoRouter>((ref) {
  return GoRouter(
    initialLocation: '/',
    refreshListenable: authNotifier,  // Refresh on auth changes
    redirect: (context, state) {
      // Auth redirect logic
    },
    routes: [
      GoRoute(path: '/', builder: (context, state) => const WelcomeScreen()),
      GoRoute(path: '/login', builder: (context, state) => const LoginScreen()),
      GoRoute(path: '/dashboard', builder: (context, state) => const DashboardScreen()),
      // Modal/overlay routes with fade transition
      GoRoute(
        path: '/settings',
        pageBuilder: (context, state) => CustomTransitionPage(
          key: state.pageKey,
          child: const SettingsScreen(),
          transitionsBuilder: (context, animation, _, child) =>
              FadeTransition(opacity: animation, child: child),
          opaque: false,
        ),
      ),
    ],
  );
});
```

**Navigation:**
```dart
context.go('/dashboard');      // Replace current route
context.push('/settings');     // Push on top
context.pop();                 // Go back
context.go('/error-alert', extra: 'Error message');  // Pass data
```

