## Code Generation

Run when modifying Freezed, Built Value, or Chopper files:

```bash
flutter pub run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs
```

**Generated files (do NOT edit):**
- `*.freezed.dart` - Freezed state classes
- `*.g.dart` - JSON serialization, Built Value
- `*.chopper.dart` - Chopper service implementations

